snippet.title: Age of Darkness: Final Stand Full Release Announcement trailer – PC Gaming Show: Most Wanted 2024
snippet.description:
Dark fantasy RTS Age of Darkness: Final Stand is getting a full release this winter, letting you experience its uncompromising strategy action in campaign, multiplayer, and survival modes. It’ll quite literally give you Nightmares. Hundreds of ‘em, in fact.
